{
  "texts": [
    "-Duplicates, missing course grades, courses taken multiple times, and grades other than letter (A-F) or pass/ fail grades were removed.",
    "-Random Forest model was implemented.",
    "-Weighted each instance with the inverse of its label proportion to achieve label balance in the training set.",
    "-Indicator value of -999 imputed for missing standardized test scores.",
    "-To improve fairness, different threshold values for each subgroup was set such that equality of opportunity is achieved in the testing set."
  ]
}